# L-01: nuclei-templates should be a git submodule (large YAML data ~1.5M LOC)

# L-02: argus-platform/ was removed during v5 migration — no longer needed.

# Windows Redis binaries — shipped for legacy start-argus.ps1 support
# but should not be tracked in git (22MB+ of binary bloat).
redis/*.exe
redis/*.dll

# Windows reserved device names — accidental artifacts from piped output
nul
NUL

# Accidental version artifacts from pip freeze or similar commands
=*
argus-workers/=*
